title: $:/plugins/tiddlywiki/codemirror-autocomplete/readme

This plugin enhances the [[CodeMirror|http://codemirror.net]] text editor with Autocompletion functionality. It needs the latest [[CodeMirror plugin|$:/plugins/tiddlywiki/codemirror]] to be installed

It adds Autocompletion for ''html'', ''javascript'' and ''xml'' and also for ''already present words'' within a text-editor instance

>To enable the Autocompletion ~AddOn, copy the following lines and ''append'' them at the bottom of the ''require'' section in $:/config/CodeMirror<br>

>Then make sure that all entries except the last one within the ''require'' section end with a 'semicolon'

<$macrocall $name="copy-to-clipboard-above-right" src='		"$:/plugins/tiddlywiki/codemirror/addon/hint/show-hint.js",
		"$:/plugins/tiddlywiki/codemirror/addon/hint/anyword-hint.js",
		"$:/plugins/tiddlywiki/codemirror/addon/hint/css-hint.js",
		"$:/plugins/tiddlywiki/codemirror/addon/hint/xml-hint.js",
		"$:/plugins/tiddlywiki/codemirror/addon/hint/html-hint.js",
		"$:/plugins/tiddlywiki/codemirror/addon/hint/javascript-hint.js"'/>

```json
		"$:/plugins/tiddlywiki/codemirror/addon/hint/show-hint.js",
		"$:/plugins/tiddlywiki/codemirror/addon/hint/anyword-hint.js",
		"$:/plugins/tiddlywiki/codemirror/addon/hint/css-hint.js",
		"$:/plugins/tiddlywiki/codemirror/addon/hint/xml-hint.js",
		"$:/plugins/tiddlywiki/codemirror/addon/hint/html-hint.js",
		"$:/plugins/tiddlywiki/codemirror/addon/hint/javascript-hint.js"
```

>Then copy the following lines and ''append'' them at the bottom of the ''configuration'' section in $:/config/CodeMirror<br>

>Make sure that all entries except the last one within the ''require'' section end with a 'semicolon'

<$macrocall $name="copy-to-clipboard-above-right" src='		"extraKeys": {
			"Ctrl-Space": "autocomplete"
		}'/>

```json
		"extraKeys": {
			"Ctrl-Space": "autocomplete"
		}
```

>You can change "Ctrl-Space" and use your own shortcut for autocompletion<br>

> ''Save'' and ''Reload'' your wiki to have the changes take effect
